WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.441 --> 00:00:01.872
Inventory management

2
00:00:01.872 --> 00:00:03.432
includes the activities employed

3
00:00:03.432 --> 00:00:05.245
in maintaining the optimum amount

4
00:00:05.245 --> 00:00:07.480
of each inventory item.

5
00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:09.613
The objective of inventory management

6
00:00:09.613 --> 00:00:12.032
is to provide uninterrupted customer service

7
00:00:12.032 --> 00:00:13.903
at the minimum cost.

8
00:00:13.903 --> 00:00:15.527
How does inventory management

9
00:00:15.527 --> 00:00:18.068
play a part in customer service?

10
00:00:18.068 --> 00:00:20.149
By having continuous conversations

11
00:00:20.149 --> 00:00:21.694
with the lab staff,

12
00:00:21.694 --> 00:00:23.549
the IM can determine the true needs

13
00:00:23.549 --> 00:00:25.118
of the clinic in real time

14
00:00:25.118 --> 00:00:26.854
for the treatment of patients.

